Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.82,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.53,0:00:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.33,0:00:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.11,0:00:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.11,0:00:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.72,0:00:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.16,0:00:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.16,0:01:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.90,0:01:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.21,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.91,0:01:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.35,0:01:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.85,0:01:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.40,0:01:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,五代,給他喝個痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.47,0:01:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧!喝吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點,不要衝動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.61,0:01:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後\N我跟她的關係變成了什麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是兩天後的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.46,0:01:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,我很驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她居然能如此坦率地\N接受我的愛的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說郁子的英文考了92分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,原來是這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.77,0:02:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該早點告訴我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.31,0:02:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後也拜託你好好教郁子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.61,0:02:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她之間的裂痕\N也總算修復了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.59,0:02:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#10 海灘愛情恐慌!\N情敵討厭小狗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要送去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看\N那是二丁目的大葉先生要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子真好啊,閒閒沒事幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?不要看不起小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子也有小孩子的煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會有什麼煩惱嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗髮精,洗髮精…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,忘記帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天碰到你很多次耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在是暑假啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好慘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.69,0:04:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師說暑假有出去玩的話\N要把它寫在圖畫日記裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.22,0:04:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我媽又是那個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸到了假日\N也好像很累的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!你家有爸爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.83,0:04:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連你這個房客也很少看到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.44,0:04:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這倒是讓我想起小時候的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我也有同樣的功課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行的話\N要把那個地方的地圖畫下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有去旅行的人\N就交一篇自由研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.02,0:04:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們家是開店的\N全家都在店裡忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.75,0:04:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也每天都被叫到店裡幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫自由研究的,只有五代耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好慘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好恨會出這種鬼作業的\N那個沒大腦的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,現在還有學校\N會出這種作業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說,很痛苦的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是家庭不好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,我要學壞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去海邊玩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?你真的要帶我去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.19,0:05:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,媽媽,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說,大哥哥說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪個大哥哥啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的五代哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.03,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥說要帶我去海邊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧?讓我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員也一起去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,妳跟去的話\N我也比較放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人多比較好玩啊\N好啦,去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧,去吧,去吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了\N可以一起去海邊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個嗜好還真有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著自己的游泳褲\N有那麼舒服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾回去!你這個變態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼變成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要教郁子游泳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.62,0:07:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我在電話跟她說了\N她就堅持要跟著來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子沒有關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那傢伙叫來的是大嬸吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以省下電車費啊\N你這個窮學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,你那麼忙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.81,0:07:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,今天我剛好也很想游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.11,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常的日子竟然有時間去海邊玩\N你還真是閒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.15,0:08:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟上班族不一樣\N我的時間比較自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有學生那麼自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也要打工很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.86,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你終於要買腳踏車了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那麼奢侈享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是賺生活費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.33,0:08:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還真是罕見,不過很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的時候吃點苦是很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.01,0:08:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我還很年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.04,0:08:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸你的\N也只有年輕這一項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕就有可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.15,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲\N拿看不見的未來當擋箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.31,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個白痴,大白痴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車子好少喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.72,0:09:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,照這種速度\N大概兩個小時就能到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有狗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是我們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹嘛把牠帶來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為惣一郎也想到海邊玩水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋,這樣已經超載了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能讓牠下車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗應該不算在人數裡面吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真頭痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要停在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開車會累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉色不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是折回去比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我已經好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,請妳先回車上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟他說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,我馬上就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想在這裡一決勝負是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你會開車嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?到底會不會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只會騎腳踏車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個?你是指狗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,就是狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你怕狗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候被狗嚇過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點都不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我在開車喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下真的事態嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,你的臉色又發白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.93,0:12:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎\N說不定我馬上就會去陪你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著真的太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,開車那麼粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛,我還以為死定了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是那個意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,走吧走吧\N我們去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員也一起來玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再稍微休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們先去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這麼弱不禁風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把狗帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.85,0:13:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,我就仗義相助救你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,惣一郎,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.45,0:13:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎好像很喜歡三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠真的很喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠一旦喜歡上一個人\N就會一直黏著他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抱著你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,對不起,很重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,一點都不重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.18,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這傢伙在\N他就不能接近管理員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大好機會,大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,你幫我看一下惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員,妳要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想游到深一點的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一個人不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嬸嬸很會游泳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不,凡事要預防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有幾年沒來海邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然跟我裝蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個女孩子太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一碰上色狼就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太大膽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道因為我是寡婦的關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我要跟你說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個寡婦沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒打算裝什麼純情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是水母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是水母啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭\N原來剛才那個是水母啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.97,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N原來妳是用那種眼光在看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳就一個人慢慢游吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是個危險的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.55,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以算了\N你在生氣不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,要不要上來坐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種冷漠的男朋友\N不要理他啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.50,0:16:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.84,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒釣到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還在生氣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悶不吭聲地讓人覺得好恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們看起來像一對情侶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的恢復力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,那是什麼啊,好遜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,過來,我們去玩沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,兩位小姐\N你們是從哪裡來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,三鷹\N你的身體沒事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,已經完全好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.84,0:17:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位小姐\N我的女伴回來了,失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就住在那間飯店裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚請過來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾,我今天就要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真無趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是受歡迎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是容易受女孩子\N玩弄的類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去划船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去划吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賴皮鬼,居然你們大人自己去划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我們馬上就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的風景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊的景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來教妳如何划船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像蠻好玩的\N可是我學得會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳坐到我的旁邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.82,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定馬上就能學會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一下子就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩手握著划槳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握的方法有點不太對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看,要像這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全無視我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把槳稍微壓低一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,稍微再…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?橡皮艇不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.62,0:19:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才聽見惣一郎的叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?\N剛才那個叫聲不是我裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,牠要被沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,看我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N三鷹,拜託你快把船划過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,乖喔乖喔,已經沒事了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把惣一郎帶到船上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你囉,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁,那我先回去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,接下來就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我…我想去坐橡皮艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.29,0:20:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體又不舒服了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太沒用了\N居然連划個船也會暈船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點回去的話要天黑了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋\N我也很擔心一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還是不行的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我來開車嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.84,0:21:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外啊\N想不到妳有駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.58,0:21:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我考上駕照以後\N從來都沒有上路的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.52,0:21:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得能不能開得好\N因為我沒辦法分心看後視鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.72,0:22:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我坐在前座幫忙妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.09,0:22:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是前座的死亡率最高耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.83,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能死在妳的手裡\N我也死而無憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員請繫上安全帶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎,發動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在…在跑了耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,開慢一點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.61,0:22:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.54,0:22:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要講話!我會分心的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.98,0:22:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.09,0:23:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員開車很有男子氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超了好多台車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.46,0:23:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟郁子都很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.27,0:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是五代哥哥和網球教練\N卻嚇得全身發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.67,0:23:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,問大家一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.27,0:23:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起來\N心頭都會一陣悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.44,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有種酸酸甜甜的感覺\N這是什麼回憶呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案是初戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.34,0:23:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.08,0:24:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『賢太郎的初戀!\N只要有愛年齡不是問題』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.78,0:24:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早熟的賢太郎\N他的初戀情人究竟是誰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.90,0:24:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.05,0:24:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.05,0:24:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能讓我悸動不已
